loving it.

1:24:07.143 --> 1:24:08.475
An action fight.

1:24:08.477 --> 1:24:10.477
Shit. What the hell?

1:24:10.479 --> 1:24:11.779
What did I do?

1:24:13.883 --> 1:24:15.883
You didn't do anything wrong.
Don't worry.

1:24:15.885 --> 1:24:19.286
- They want me.
- What did you do?

1:24:19.288 --> 1:24:20.521
Come on.

1:24:24.126 --> 1:24:25.993
Right-hand lead.
